rComments: Gary is a bit difficult to speak with & a bit difficult to predict. I got an A thanks to my genuine interest, but I often felt foolish in front of him. His studies in translated literature may not carry much clout in some critical spheres, but he has a special and very valuable type of genius/outlook. I confess he deserves a hot rating as well.
Prof. Adelman is the most passionate and brilliant scholar that I have ever had the pleasure of knowing.  Also, he has a disarming voice that matches perfectly his devilish good looks.
